==German==

===Pronunciation===
/ʃarf/

===Etymology===
Old High German ''[[scarf]]'', akin to Old Saxon ''skarp'', compare Dutch ''[[scherp]]''

===Adjective===
'''scharf''' (schärfer, schärfst)

# [[sharp]] (knife, intellect)
# [[hot]] (spicy)
# [[nipping]]
# [[hot]] (sexy)

